Available Tools: list_commits | get_commit | create_branch | delete_branch | list_branches | compare_branches
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "owner": "string", "repo": "string", "branch": "string", "sha": "string" }
Response Schema: { "commits": [{ "sha": "string", "message": "string", "author": "string", "date": "string" }], "branch": "string" }
---
Question: Display all branches for the nexus-dynamics/ai-engine repository.
Call: { "func_call": "list_branches", "owner": "nexus-dynamics", "repo": "ai-engine", "branch": "", "sha": "" }
Response: { "commits": [], "branch": "main" }

Question: Initialize a new hotfix branch named hotfix/memory-leak in the nexus-dynamics/ai-engine repo based on commit 7x8y9z0a.
Call: { "func_call": "create_branch", "owner": "nexus-dynamics", "repo": "ai-engine", "branch": "hotfix/memory-leak", "sha": "7x8y9z0a" }
Response: { "commits": [], "branch": "hotfix/memory-leak" }

Question: Remove the obsolete experimental branch exp/neural-net-v1 from the nexus-dynamics/ai-engine project.
Call: { "func_call": "delete_branch", "owner": "nexus-dynamics", "repo": "ai-engine", "branch": "exp/neural-net-v1", "sha": "" }
Response: { "commits": [], "branch": "exp/neural-net-v1" }

